    <description><![CDATA[Courthouse Square, Hwy. 82, Dickens (marker is inside of courthouse)<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 512 Montgomery St., Dickens<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> --]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-100.836338,33.621313,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Red Mud Cemetery</name>
    <description><![CDATA[from Spur, SW on FM 261 to CR 496<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> CR 496, Spur]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-100.999246,33.426696,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Document>
